title: (Photo Inserted) Ornament For Dog Who Passed Away - Personalized Suncatcher Ornament
body_html:
Keep your furry friend close to your heart with our Dog Character Memorial Personalized Suncatcher Ornament. The perfect keepsake to honor the memory of a beloved dog! This beautiful suncatcher is personalized with the dog's breed, name, and date. It features the saying "If love could have saved you, you would have lived forever".
The front of this suncatcher is laser engraved on wood and mounted on stained glass acrylic. The acrylic stained glass will vary in design and color for each piece.

MESSAGE: If love could have saved you, you would have lived forever.

 PRODUCT DETAILS:
  • The front of this suncatcher is made from premium natural wood and mounted on acrylic plexiglass.
  • Size: 3.54 x 3.29 inches, 4 x 3.7 inches.
  • Thickness: 6mm.
  • 1-sided design.
  • Coir rope included for hanging.

title: Welcome Foolish Mortals - Dog Version - Personalized Doormat
body_html:
Personalized doormats are the perfect way to welcome guests and add personality to your home! Customize with names, inspirational quotes, or fun images for a one-of-a-kind style. Durable and customizable, design your own stylish mat to make a great first impression.

Welcome guests to your perfect home with our customizable dog-lover doormats which are special versions for Halloween! Ideal for any dog mom, dog dad. These whimsical mats allow you to proudly display your love for all things dogs right at your doorstep.
These mats are perfect for Halloween to show off your dog obsession! Durable enough for daily use, your doormat will showcase your unique style while keeping your entryway clean. The perfect gift for the dog lover in your life or to treat yourself!
Show your neighbors and guests your undying love for dogs with a custom doormat made just for you. A perfect memento for any dog mom, dad, or enthusiast!

MESSAGE: Welcome Foolish Mortals.

PRODUCT DETAILS:

  • Each doormat is made from luxurious plush velour and features a premium heat dye sublimation print for long-lasting color vibrancy.
  • The underside is constructed from high-quality epoxy for a non-slip grip and extra durability.
  •  Our doormats are widely used for home decor, kitchen, bedroom, living room, office, and more.
  • Care Instructions: Use a damp cloth with mild soapy water to clean (avoid bleach) and let air dry. We recommend a light vacuuming of the rug to assist in the settling process.
  • Size: 24 x 16 inch, 30 x 20 inch and 36 x 24 inch.
  • Thickness: 4mm - 5mm
  • Due to manual measurement, some difference is unavoidable. Please be tolerant!

title: Living My Best Life - Personalized Shirt
body_html:
Looking for the perfect birthday gift or Christmas present for a Black queen in your life? Look no further! This personalized shirt embodies the essence of being a strong and majestic Black woman, making it an ideal gift that will inspire and uplift. With this Living My Best Life - Personalized Shirt black power shirt, you declare that you are more than what society labels you – you are a force to be reckoned with, a beacon of resilience and pride. Embrace your identity as a queen, unapologetically and with grace. This shirt is more than just fashion; it's a statement of empowerment and cultural significance. The striking design features a beautiful illustration of Afro hair

MESSAGE: Living My Best Life.

PRODUCT DETAILS:

  • 100% cotton (99% for ash/grey colors, 50% for hoodie)
  • Decoration type: Digital Print

title: A Lifetime Of Love And Adventures - Personalized Enamel Mug
body_html:
You're gonna love this Personalized Enamel Mug! It's all about a lifetime of love and adventures with a cute forest design. This mug is perfect gift for announcing your engagement, celebrating anniversaries, or giving as a keepsake to wedding guests. And guess what? It's super durable, making it the ideal camp mug for all those awesome outdoor trips. Plus, with your own personal touch, it becomes a heartwarming gift for both you and your partner, showing off your love for each other. So grab this enchanting mug and let it be a sweet reminder of your endless love and all those amazing moments you've shared in the great outdoors!

MESSAGE:  

A lifetime of love and adventures.

PRODUCT DETAILS:

  • Stainless steel with enamel finish.
  • 12oz fluid capacity.
  • 3.2” height x 3.25” diameter.
  • Full-color printing.
  • Hand washing with mild detergent is recommended.

title: I'm The Oldest Sister Middle Sister Youngest Sister - Personalized Shirt
body_html:
Celebrate the bond of sisterhood with our adorable matching sibling shirts! Whether you're the big sister, middle sister, or youngest sister, these family matching shirts are a delightful way to show off your special connection. Crafted with premium materials, our shirts are designed for comfort and style, making them perfect for family outings or special occasions. Choose from "Big Sister," "Middle Sister," or "Youngest Sister" designs to match each sibling's unique role. It becomes a truly unique and thoughtful gift, suitable for Christmas, birthdays, Valentine's Day, Father’s Day, Mother's Day, Pet's Day, and even anniversaries.

  • I'm the Oldest Sister I Make The Rules.
  • I'm The Middle Sister I'm The Reason We Have The Rules.
  • I'm The Youngest Sister The Rules Don't Apply To Me.
